1845  AlignmentSelector(int val) : value((uint8_t)val) {}
1846  operator uint8_t() const { return value; }
1847  AlignmentSelector& operator=(uint8_t val) { value = val; return *this; }
1848  AlignmentSelector& operator=(int val) { value = val; return *this; }
1849  AlignmentSelector& operator|=(uint8_t val) { return *this = value | val; }
1850  AlignmentSelector& operator&=(uint8_t val) { return *this = value & val; }
